==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polygonaceous
<hw>Pol`y*go*na"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Polygonum</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to a
natural order of apetalous plants (<ord>Polygonace⟦ae⟧</ord>), of which
the knotweeds (species of <gen>Polygonum</gen>) are the type, and which
includes also the docks (<gen>Rumex</gen>), the buckwheat, rhubarb, sea
grape (<gen>Coccoloba</gen>), and several other genera.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polygonal</ent>⟦br⟧
